<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="my">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
    <title>Emergency Calls - Global</title>
    
    <link rel="manifest" href="manifest.json">
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black-translucent">
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-title" content="Emergency">
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#b91c1c">
    
    <style>
        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        body { font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif; background: #b91c1c; color: #fff; min-height: 100vh; }
        .container { max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 1rem; }
        .header { text-align: center; padding: 2rem 0 1rem; }
        .header h1 { font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }
        .header p { opacity: 0.8; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        .lang-select { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        .lang-select button { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); border: none; color: #fff; padding: 0.4rem 1rem; border-radius: 20px; cursor: pointer; font-size: 0.85rem; }
        .lang-select button.active { background: #fff; color: #b91c1c; font-weight: bold; }
        .search-box { width: 100%; padding: 0.8rem 1rem; border-radius: 25px; border: none; font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); color: #fff; outline: none; }
        .search-box::placeholder { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); }
        .country-card { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); backdrop-filter: blur(5px); border-radius: 16px; padding: 1rem; margin-bottom: 0.8rem; }
        .country-header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }
        .country-name { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: bold; }
        .country-capital { font-size: 0.75rem; opacity: 0.7; }
        .number-list { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.4rem; margin-top: 0.5rem; }
        .call-btn { background: #fff; color: #b91c1c; font-weight: bold; padding: 0.5rem 0.8rem; border-radius: 30px; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.85rem; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.3rem; }
        .call-btn:active { transform: scale(0.95); }
        .no-results { text-align: center; padding: 2rem; opacity: 0.7; }
        .footer { text-align: center; padding: 2rem 0 1rem; opacity: 0.5; font-size: 0.75rem; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="header">
        <h1 id="title">🚨 အရေးပေါ်ခေါ်ဆိုရန်</h1>
        <p id="subtitle">နိုင်ငံရွေးချယ်ပြီး ဖုန်းခေါ်ဆိုနိုင်ပါသည်</p>
        <div class="lang-select">
            <button class="active" data-lang="my" onclick="setLang('my')">မြန်မာ</button>
            <button data-lang="en" onclick="setLang('en')">English</button>
        </div>
        <input type="text" class="search-box" id="searchInput" oninput="renderList()" placeholder="🔍 နိုင်ငံအမည်ရှာရန်...">
    </div>
    <div id="countryList"></div>
    <div class="footer">Global Emergency Numbers | ကမ္ဘာလုံးဆိုင်ရာ အရေးပေါ်နံပါတ်များ | ၁၉၀+ နိုင်ငံ</div>
</div>

